    <div class="alpheios-lex-entry" lemma-id="n1329" body-key="α">
          <b><span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἀπο-τί̄νω</span></b> , fut. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἀποτίσεις</span>, inf. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">-σέμεν</span>, aor. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἀπέτῑσε,
          -αν</span>, mid. fut. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἀποτί̄σομαι</span>,
          aor. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἀπετί̄σατο</span>, subj. <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἀποτί̄σεαι</span>: I. act., <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">pay back, pay
            for, atone for;</span>
          <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">τῑμὴν Ἀργείοις ἀποτῑνέμεν,</span>
          <i><span class="en">Il. 3.286</span></i>; <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">
            εὐεργεσίᾱς ἀποτί̄νειν,</span>
          <i><span class="en">Od. 22.235</span></i>; <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">
            τριπλῇ τετραπλῇ τ᾽ ἀποτί̄σομεν</span>, ‘will make good,’ <i><span class="en">Il. 1.128</span></i>.—II. mid. (Od.), <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">exact
            payment</span> (see under <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἀποτί̄νυμαι</span>) or <span class="alpheios-lex-gloss">satisfaction, avenge oneself upon,
            punish</span> (<span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">τί</span> or <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">τινά</span>); <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">κείνων γε βιᾶς
            ἀποτίσεαι ἐλθών,</span>
          <i><span class="en">Od. 11.118</span></i>; <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">
            ἀπετί̄σατο ποινὴν</span> | <span class="alpheios-lex-greek" lang="grc">ἰφθί̄μων
            ἑτάρων</span>, ‘for’ them, <i><span class="en">Od.
            24.312</span></i>.</div> <div class="alpheios-lex-footnotes en"> </div>
